  <description><![CDATA[<div id="descriptionAccTop" class="c-page-content u-margin-bottom u-overflow-hidden">
<p>The Hotel Cristal Lodge is an eclectic Alpine hotel with a central location in<span> </span><span>Chantemerle, one of the main districts of Serre Chevalier. The hotel benefits from being a short walk away from the ski lifts and resort centre, where you can find a range of shops, bars and restaurants. After a day of adventures, head back to the hotel for a drink or two at the tapas bar, or unwind in the wellness area.</span><span></span></p>
<h2><span>Cosy and comfortable</span></h2>
<p><span>The hotel has a modern feel to it, with eclectic touches including disco balls and a phone box adorning the lobby and reception area. The apartments are excellent choice for groups of families and friends looking for self catering apartments in Serre Chevalier. We offer apartments which can sleep up to eight people, with each apartment having its own fully equipped kitchen, lounge area and comfortable bedrooms. The apartments are furnished in a simplistic Alpine design, and provide a comfortable place to stay in a great location. </span></p>
<h2><span>Family friendly</span></h2>
<p><span>The lounge area is a great spot to chill after a day of skiing or snowboarding, there is also a playroom for the little ones and a nearby Savoyard style tapas bar - perfect for sampling some of the regions specialities. </span></p>
<h2><span>Unwind and relax</span></h2>
<p>After a day of skiing or snowboarding on the slopes of <a data-udi="umb://document/b7e31f4645514434bec76a3728e974c0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b7e31f4645514434bec76a3728e974c0}" title="Serre Chevalier">Serre Chevalier</a>, relax and rejuvenate at the wellness facilities included with your stay. Unwind and recharge in the sauna and hammam, or take a soak in the hot tub to ease any aches and pains. For a moment of complete and utter relaxation, spoil yourself with a spa treatment or massage.</p>
</div>]]></description>
