  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>One bedroom + cabin apartments</strong> are around 49-55m²and sleep two to six people. These apartments have one double bedroom and a small cabin room with bunk beds, and an additional pull out sofa bed in the lounge.  </p>
<p><strong>Two bedroom apartments</strong> are around 54-66m² and sleep two to six people. These apartments have one double bedroom and one twin or double bedroom, and an additional double pull out sofa bed in the lounge.</p>
<p><strong>Two bedroom + cabin apartments</strong> are around 64-71m² and sleep two to eight people. These apartments have one double room, one twin bedroom,  a small cabin room with bunk beds and an additional pull out sofa bed in the lounge. Some apartments may have two WCs. </p>
<p><strong>Apartment facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Lounge</li>
<li>Free Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Balcony or terrace</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>One bathroom with shower or bath</li>
<li>Fully equipped kitchenette with fridge, oven, microwave, grill, ceramic hobs, dishwasher</li>
<li>Tea and coffee making facilities</li>
<li>Cleaning kit </li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Beds are made on arrival</li>
<li>End of stay cleaning is included except the kitchen</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>]]></roomsDescription>
